Gyoto has been written starting in 2008 primarily by:
 Frédéric Vincent [1, 2]
 Thibaut Paumard [1]
 Nicolas Aimar [1]

Additional contributors:
 Odele Straub [1]
 Frédéric Lamy [2]
 Irene Urso [1]
 Paloma Thévenet [1]

The development team at Observatoire de Paris also includes:
 Éric Gourgoulhon [2]
 Guy Perrin [1]

The implementation of the Balasin-Grumiller metric has been written by
Filipe Costa [3,4]
José Natário [4]

